<section class="container" style="max-width:900px;margin:36px auto;padding:18px">
  <h1>{{title}}</h1>
  <p style="color:#666">Last updated: 2025-11-16</p>

  <p>If you want your ZimEduFinder account and personal data removed, follow one of the options below. We will process deletion requests within 48 hours where possible.</p>

  <h2>Option 1 — Email request (recommended)</h2>
  <p>Send an email to <a href="mailto:support@skoolfinder.net">support@skoolfinder.net</a> with the subject line <strong>Delete My Account</strong> and include the email address you used to sign in. We will confirm and delete your account and associated data.</p>

  <h2>Option 2 — Deauthorize via your provider</h2>
  <p>If you signed in with Facebook or Google you can remove the app's access from their account settings. After deauthorisation, email us with the same subject line and we will delete your data on request.</p>

  <h2>What will be deleted</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Account record</li>
    <li>Saved preferences and favourites</li>
    <li>Provider identifiers (Google/Facebook IDs)</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Note: Aggregated anonymised analytics may be retained for product improvement.</p>

  <h2>Questions</h2>
  <p>Contact <a href="mailto:support@skoolfinder.net">support@skoolfinder.net</a> for help.</p>
</section>
